Build Instructions:

Needed external libraries:
Slick:  http://slick.ninjacave.com/
    Jars needed: jinput.jar , lwjgl.jar , lwjgl_util.jar , slick.jar (added as external jars to the build path)
LWJGL Bundle:  https://sourceforge.net/projects/java-game-lib/files/latest/download?source=files
    Connect native library files for your system (windows etc.) as the native files for slick.jar in the build path
	
Then download all class files from the "Cole branch" into eclipse using the buildpath specified above.
